{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"description","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/description","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/background_color\">background_color</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/categories\">categories</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/description\">description</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/display\">display</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/display_override\">display_override</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/icons\">icons</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/name\">name</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/orientation\">orientation</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/prefer_related_applications\">prefer_related_applications</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/protocol_handlers\">protocol_handlers</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/related_applications\">related_applications</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/scope\">scope</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/screenshots\">screenshots</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/short_name\">short_name</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/shortcuts\">shortcuts</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/start_url\">start_url</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/theme_color\">theme_color</a></li></ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">型</th>\n      <td><code>String</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">必須</th>\n      <td>いいえ</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p><em><code>description</code></em> メンバーは、何をするアプリケーションなのかを開発者が説明することができる文字列です。 <code>description</code> には書字方向を設定することができ、マニフェストメンバーの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest\"><code>dir</code></a> と <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest\"><code>lang</code></a> の値に基づいて左書きまたは右書きで表示することができます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>左書き言語用の単純な <code>description</code> です。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: json notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">\"description\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Awesome application that will help you achieve your dreams.\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>アラビア語の <code>description</code> で、右書きで表示されます。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: json notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">\"dir\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"rtl\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">\"lang\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">\"description\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\".تطبيق رائع سيساعدك على تحقيق أحلامك\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/manifest-app-info/#description-member","title":"Web App Manifest - Application Information"}],"query":"html.manifest.description"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"html.manifest.description","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/description/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"}],"summary":"description メンバーは、何をするアプリケーションなのかを開発者が説明することができる文字列です。 description には書字方向を設定することができ、マニフェストメンバーの dir と lang の値に基づいて左書きまたは右書きで表示することができます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"description","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"description","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/mani